<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_bdd70c0f-aa1c-475b-94e9-d222cc77117c" outputclass="ncc-clause" variation="SA"><sptc>I3D3</sptc><title id="_03a399eb-0159-47ab-a3c4-02b58c38fa75">Provision for escape</title><subclause id="_f02635b2-d30e-4aa7-ad8e-fd8b924b5f9f" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_d1aa5298-8620-4ac8-babc-b299e3e61442">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>Exit travel distances in a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1271_2.5.0.xml#_f68a626d-6a81-4785-95fa-c032c987c28e" id="_c7238aaf-ab84-46ec-a2c1-d70f8be14b56" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">farm building</xref> must comply with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1491_1.6.0.xml#_bc3de888-9e88-4486-b7ee-3f03a531f5da" id="_572b92b6-348c-4e3a-b14d-adb92c47c2d1" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-clause">D2D5</xref> except—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_e303506e-3841-4720-bbc1-a61b05609bdb">no point on the floor must be more than 20 m from an exit, or a point from which travel in different directions to 2 exits is available, in which case the maximum distance to one of those exits must not exceed 60 m; and</li><li id="_959f3fa3-bbfa-451a-a449-ad501e905d13">in a machinery room, plant room or the like, the distance to a single exit serving a storey at the level of access to a road or open space may be increased to 30 m.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_ee2393e2-3e81-429a-a5ea-c7003d0684ef" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_93f05817-9787-467f-b6ca-1568eb29768e">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>Exits that are required as alternative means of egress in a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1271_2.5.0.xml#_f68a626d-6a81-4785-95fa-c032c987c28e" id="_9832187d-e29d-41a1-a48f-af35a38a07fe" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">farm building</xref> must be in accordance with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1493_1.3.0.xml#_2cf6ef94-e857-412e-a2db-fa69d562c657" id="_f3c3a1bd-7708-429b-8449-746145bf7cbf" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-clause">D2D6</xref> except they must not be more than 80 m apart.</p></subclause></clause>